            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and<strong> half </strong>the<strong> chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong> and <strong>kidney beans</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> drained beans </strong>and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lime </strong>and cook for a further 2 min – this is your <strong>double bean & butternut squash</strong> <strong>chilli</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1612277929645-x200.jpg",
