            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>double bean & butternut squash</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and top with the <strong>browned</strong> <strong>tortilla triangles</strong></p><p>Tip: Make sure some of them are spiking up for extra crunch, the bottom bits will soak up all that yummy sauce!</p><p>Put the <strong>tortilla-topped double bean & butternut squash chilli </strong>in the oven for 5-6 min or until the tortilla triangles are nice and crispy</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1612277938850-x200.jpg",
