            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tortilla-topped double bean & butternut squash chilli is in the oven, trim, then chop the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> roughly</p><p>Combine the<strong> remaining chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>with the <strong>mayo</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1612277946266-x200.jpg",
