            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1612277946266-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomato</strong> over the top of the tortilla-topped double bean & butternut squash chilli and drizzle over the <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p><p>Set the <strong>tortilla-topped double bean & butternut squash chilli</strong> in the centre of the table and garnish with the <strong>lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
